winning Madam Zhang’s sympathy.

150
00:07:31,759 --> 00:07:34,600
Gradually, we became the best servants in Zhang Mansion.

151
00:07:35,160 --> 00:07:35,959
But

152
00:07:36,639 --> 00:07:39,079
we never forgot our revenge for even a moment.

153
00:07:43,560 --> 00:07:46,040
I used poison to make them hallucinate,

154
00:07:46,759 --> 00:07:48,480
then used the little ghost to frighten them.

155
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:51,079
Madam Zhang was timid, so she died quickly.

156
00:07:51,160 --> 00:07:51,759
Xie Xin.

157
00:07:52,120 --> 00:07:53,360
Master Zhang has a tough life,

158
00:07:53,600 --> 00:07:54,800
