159
00:07:55,839 --> 00:07:58,319
We used the little ghost to scare off the other servants.

160
00:07:58,920 --> 00:08:01,639
I want to wipe out the Zhang family’s bloodline.

161
00:08:02,120 --> 00:08:05,319
I want Master Zhang to suffer the pain of sacrificial piling too.

162
00:08:06,199 --> 00:08:07,639
I want them

163
