The bullets are over here.

187
00:09:14,279 --> 00:09:15,080
Stop this now.

188
00:09:16,399 --> 00:09:18,320
You two, husband and wife, will come to the station with me and surrender.

189
00:09:18,600 --> 00:09:20,039
The injustice done to Da Bao and Xiao Bao

190
